{"info":{"author":null,"author_email":"Jordan Anderson <paul.jordan.anderson@gmail.com>","bugtrack_url":null,"classifiers":[],"description":"# e4b\n\n**Alias for [`experts4bit-qlora`](https://pypi.org/project/experts4bit-qlora/).**\n\n```bash\npip install e4b\n```\n```python\nimport e4b   # identical to `import experts4bit_qlora`\n```\n\n`e4b` is one of several short/variant names for **experts4bit-qlora** —\nQLoRA fine-tuning of fused 4-bit Mixture-of-Experts on a single small GPU, on\nstock bitsandbytes. This package is a thin alias so the name resolves instead\nof dead-ending; all code, docs, and releases live in the real package.\n\n- Real package: https://pypi.org/project/experts4bit-qlora/\n- Source: https://github.com/pjordanandrsn/experts4bit-qlora\n- Project home: https://cerinamroth.com/ml/\n\nExtras forward: `pip install e4b[train]` / `[serve]`. MIT © Cerin Amroth.\n","description_content_type":"text/markdown","docs_url":null,"download_url":null,"downloads":{"last_day":-1,"last_month":-1,"last_week":-1},"dynamic":["License-File"],"home_page":null,"keywords":"experts4bit, e4b, bitsandbytes, qlora, moe, mixture-of-experts, quantization, nf4, alias","license":"MIT","license_expression":null,"license_files":["LICENSE"],"maintainer":null,"maintainer_email":null,"name":"e4b","package_url":"https://pypi.org/project/e4b/","platform":null,"project_url":"https://pypi.org/project/e4b/","project_urls":{"Homepage":"https://cerinamroth.com/ml/","Real package (experts4bit-qlora)":"https://pypi.org/project/experts4bit-qlora/","Source":"https://github.com/pjordanandrsn/experts4bit-qlora"},"provides_extra":["train","serve"],"release_url":"https://pypi.org/project/e4b/0.1.0/","requires_dist":["experts4bit-qlora>=0.2.0","experts4bit-qlora[train]>=0.2.0; extra == \"train\"","experts4bit-qlora[serve]>=0.2.0; extra == \"serve\""],"requires_python":">=3.9","summary":"Alias for experts4bit-qlora — QLoRA fine-tuning of fused 4-bit Mixture-of-Experts on a single small GPU.","versio